<h2> Definition </h2>

The adverb <strong>@HI{{amari}}</strong> expresses that the degree of the action of the verb is not great ("not much" or "not very").
<p></p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<h2> Notes </h2>

<strong>@HI{{amari}}</strong> is usually found in negative sentences.
<p></p>

@HI{{anmari}} is a variant of <strong>@HI{{amari}}</strong> sometimes found in conversation.
